# Worktree-First Workflow (Sakura ERP)

## CRITICAL: Workspace Location
- **Primary path**: `C:\Users\shahf\.cursor\worktrees\sakura-erp-system\nva`
- **Ab se sab coding YAHI worktree me hogi.**

## Workflow Rules
1. **Coding**: Sab edits isi worktree folder me karo — `ERP_Final - - Without_React2\...\frontend\`, `migrations\`, `services\`, etc.
2. **Commit & Push**: `.\sync-to-git.ps1` chalao
3. **Vercel**: Push ke baad `.\deploy-vercel-cli.ps1` (sakura-erp-system-miuq) — trigger-vercel.ps1 use mat karo
4. **Apply Button**: Composer ka "Apply" use mat karo — EPERM error. Direct prompt se edits karo.

